{"id": 2876, "genre": 1001, "title": "你在社交网络上是如何扮演一个冰山型网友的？", "description": "我所有的冷血无情，就充分体现在了我打造的高冷互联网人设上。（题图来自:视觉中国 © John Holcroft）", "record_count": 2692, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20190402170149Q7giHOuhPVCbmErs.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2019-04-05T17:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 337922, "content": "看消息就是笑而不语", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 763503}, {"id": 337923, "content": "看过，然后没了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1631081}, {"id": 338183, "content": "懒得评论，简洁回复，不发动态", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1631010}, {"id": 339208, "content": "语句简单，多发句号", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1637670}, {"id": 337674, "content": "不赞，不评论，不收藏，不关注，心里默默一笑", "image": null, "praise_count": 728, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 562149}, {"id": 337676, "content": "有时扮演，有时真是冰山，无论如何，结果就是熟人圈里无任何痕迹", "image": null, "praise_count": 53, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1402141}, {"id": 337678, "content": "玩的人好少呀，", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1629431}, {"id": 337934, "content": "只评论不回复", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1603964}, {"id": 337680, "content": "没有签名，不发动态，只关注关注我的人", "image": null, "praise_count": 66, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 282153}, {"id": 337936, "content": "就是点进来看一下，深以为之后心里一笑，感觉发言者们简直是异父异母亲兄弟——然而什么都不做就退出去顶多点个赞的你。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1630875}, {"id": 337681, "content": "不发朋友圈", "image": "img/option/option/20190406023556xTGnUpAM9DyfjauJ.jpg", "praise_count": 440, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1118099}, {"id": 337937, "content": "不喜欢发朋友圈，看得也很少了，发现自己发出来的信息经常会被人误解，感觉那就是个大家虚假伪装自己的地方。不过完全不发朋友圈，感觉自己让自己与世隔绝了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1334090}, {"id": 337682, "content": "日常潜水装死\n不发动态", "image": null, "praise_count": 143, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1118099}, {"id": 337684, "content": "不说话就完事了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 22, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1406482}, {"id": 337685, "content": "我就看看不说话", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1472617}, {"id": 337686, "content": "我就点进来看看", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1573201}, {"id": 337687, "content": "突发奇想删除朋友圈，临时性高冷。", "image": null, "praise_count": 33, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1194633}, {"id": 337688, "content": "相反\n在网上我把自己最乐观的一面给网友，但是网络毕竟是虚拟的，真正懂你的又有几个呢？", "image": "img/option/option/20190406074516AjzJ5yp2rmcXBtD0", "praise_count": 19, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1629471}, {"id": 337689, "content": "实际上我很想发表看法，但又觉得自己见识和遣词造句能力低下，所以才“被动”表现“高冷”", "image": null, "praise_count": 307, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1085613}, {"id": 337690, "content": "长期保持一年登录几次的选手，不发，不看，不点赞", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1461775}, {"id": 337691, "content": "懒得吐槽", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1601137}, {"id": 338203, "content": "我来，我看，我不说。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1611971}, {"id": 337692, "content": "不赞不评论不关注😐️", "image": null, "praise_count": 20, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1629488}, {"id": 337693, "content": "关掉朋友圈功能", "image": null, "praise_count": 103, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1629490}, {"id": 337694, "content": "不发朋友圈，不发微博，很少会评论", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1629182}, {"id": 338206, "content": "朋友圈三天可见", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1002334}, {"id": 337695, "content": "朋友圈，什么鬼？", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1616387}, {"id": 337696, "content": "没人找我我就不聊天，有人找我言简意赅", "image": null, "praise_count": 143, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1524770}, {"id": 337697, "content": "Real.时而丧 时而晴", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1613208}, {"id": 337698, "content": "有的时候连这条评论我都懒得发", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 915230}, {"id": 337700, "content": "被拉微信群后第一时间设置不提醒，然后除了同意聚会时间完全不说话", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 581109}, {"id": 337702, "content": "我来找同志们了，看看有多少冷漠的逗比", "image": "img/option/option/201904060928291mj96FgROCYucbQB", "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1434649}, {"id": 337703, "content": "喜欢的点个赞，不喜欢的嘴角一笑 划过。", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1512099}, {"id": 337704, "content": "不想回消息就不回，一言不合直接删", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1628566}, {"id": 337705, "content": "有时很很想在自己做出成绩的时候发一条“装逼”朋友圈，无奈一直没有做出成绩", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1626662}, {"id": 337706, "content": "我不是，我没有", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1629537}, {"id": 337707, "content": "关闭朋友圈", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1568899}, {"id": 337708, "content": "不发朋友圈", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1596623}, {"id": 337964, "content": "嗯", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1448905}, {"id": 338988, "content": "过10个小时再来统一回复一句🙂", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1636156}, {"id": 337709, "content": "难以想象最高赞的说的是“不评论”，那你特么的在干啥？", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1524350}, {"id": 338221, "content": "哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈都会好的好的好的回答哈哈哈好的好的好的好的好哒好哒回答回答好回答等哈等哈等哈很大很大等哈好好的好的好的好的好的很大很大很大很", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1620566}, {"id": 338733, "content": "人生如梦，往事如烟。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1635246}, {"id": 337710, "content": "我就是", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1591006}, {"id": 337966, "content": "不发任何说说朋友圈，看视频不发弹幕评论，默默点赞，默默收藏，评论，不需要的。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1631494}, {"id": 337711, "content": "测试下这个版面\n字体会怎么样排列199886678000字体的类型\n排列的方式", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1591006}, {"id": 337712, "content": "如果是这样的呢\n如果写了很多字\n入股超超除了展示屏幕\n会怎么啊拍喜讯？\n哈哈哈哈哈我也是醉了，我\n我们的\n\n我\n的\n\n我们\n\n\n\n我们都是在一起了\n\n\n我的人生态度是如此美好\n\n", "image": "img/option/option/201904061008204k7mzC5wdFjDUqXJ.jpg", "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1591006}, {"id": 337713, "content": "我在零下30°的地方上网。够冰吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 948915}, {"id": 338225, "content": "哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1626671}, {"id": 337714, "content": "哈哈哈哈这两次了\n是啊……不\n一切为了不可能是\n一个人不去想\n不过现在也可以做\n在外奔波的人要\n", "image": "img/option/option/20190406101306zVk8O2s04vlHTJr7.jpg", "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1591006}]}